---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import SectionTitle from "../components/SectionTitle.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us - VXIT">
    <main>
        <Hero
            title="About VXIT"
            subtitle="We're a passionate team of developers, designers, and digital strategists dedicated to creating exceptional web experiences that drive business growth."
        />

        <!-- Company Story Section -->
        <section class="story">
            <div class="container">
                <SectionTitle>Our Story</SectionTitle>
                <div class="story-content">
                    <div class="story-text">
                        <p>
                            Founded in 2019, VXIT emerged from a simple belief:
                            every business deserves a digital presence that not
                            only looks stunning but drives real results. What
                            started as a small team of passionate developers has
                            grown into a full-service digital agency
                            specializing in cutting-edge web development and AI
                            integration.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Our journey began when we noticed a gap in the
                            market - many agencies were creating beautiful
                            websites that lacked the technical sophistication
                            needed for modern business success. We set out to
                            bridge that gap by combining aesthetic excellence
                            with powerful functionality and emerging
                            technologies.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Today, we've helped over 100+ businesses transform
                            their digital presence, from startups launching
                            their first website to enterprises modernizing their
                            platforms with AI-powered solutions.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="story-stats">
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">100+</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Projects Completed</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">5+</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Years Experience</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Happy Clients</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat">
                            <div class="stat-number">99%</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">Client Satisfaction</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
        <section class="mission-vision">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="mission-vision-grid">
                    <div class="mission-card" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                        <p>
                            To empower businesses of all sizes with innovative
                            web solutions that combine cutting-edge technology,
                            stunning design, and measurable results. We believe
                            every business deserves a digital presence that
                            drives growth and creates lasting connections with
                            their audience.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-card" data-aos="fade-left">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                        <p>
                            To be the leading force in the evolution of web
                            development, where artificial intelligence meets
                            human creativity to create digital experiences that
                            are not just functional, but transformative. We
                            envision a future where every website is
                            intelligent, adaptive, and perfectly aligned with
                            business goals.
                        </p>
                    </div>
